tenacity-harness

one script. one soul file. one long-horizon task.

usage:

    node src/index.js "your task"

soul.md is the agent. log.txt is its history. that's it.

env: TENACITY_MODEL, OLLAMA_URL, TENACITY_MAX_TICKS, TENACITY_TICK_TIMEOUT_MS, TENACITY_CMD_TIMEOUT_MS, TENACITY_TICK_DELAY_MS.

tools: shell, write_soul, append_soul, read_file, write_file, list_files, done.
